message:
I would like to invite you to the launch of the first QR code campaign in Egypt by ShootGet in partnership with Souq.com this Tuesday at La Wien Cafe in City Stars and Wednesday at Lawien Cafe Mall of Arabia. 
ShootGet is one of Tahrir_sqr startups, that aims to create an interactive experience with static Ads.
If you wish to try it out now, Search for ShootGet in the Apple App Store or Google Play store, download the app, and try the app with this Ad.
Please like ShootGet page here so you can be updated with our latest news and offers. 
https://www.facebook.com/ShootGet
